l10n: rename 'Online Privacy Policy' to 'Privacy Policy' in the template...
l10n: rename 'Online Privacy Policy' to 'Privacy Policy' in the template (bug 747121)
resolved index.html conflict
updated about & support links in footer. fix bug 748127
Removed legacy query parameters from footer links. Fix bug 748127.
Aliased be and mn locales to Russian. Bug 742286, bug 742327.
added 'this.rate=5;' to webtrends.js. bug 744848
added WT tracking code. used output of WT tag builder - please confirm functionality. bug 744848
added tracking tags to dl URLs. fix bug 743831
added online privacy policy link to footer. fix bug 747121
Alias es-CL and es-MX to es-ES for now; alias en-GB to en-US.
Replace hl=en with hl=currentlocale everywhere. fix bug 745951.
Merge branch 'master' of github.com:mozilla/fx36start
focus search field at page load. fix bug 745949
Filter out {ok} and {l10n-extra}, no matter where they occur.
implemented Ty's CSS changes & new alert icon. bug 734197
Merge branch 'master' of github.com:mozilla/fx36start
using regex to parse browser/version. bug 744055
Strip out {ok} from translated text.
improved version checking, fixed small layout bug in search form. bug 744055
Do not generate lowercase locale directories any longer. Bug 740573 comment 15.
Removed htaccess file because of virtual host redirects. Bug 740573 comment 15.
updated width/positioning of modal to match search box below, only showing modal for version 3.6.x, added alt text to 'No thanks...' link, reduced space after 'Your browser...' headline. bug 735411
added rtl support for search box and small glowing firefox image. bug 743204
updated dl button to expand based on text length. fix bug 743206
added locale-agnostic support link. fix bug 743205
hiding upgrade message by default. showing when user NOT on PPC MacOS. fix bug 742564
removed subsetting from fonts for full character/language support. added czech locale test. fix bug 742648
Expect locale directories with dashes, not underscores.
focus search box after dismissing modal
locale/ should not be checked in.
Added htaccess file redirecting locale-based hostnames to subdirectory.
Allow adding files to the output root. Added robots.txt rejecting indexing.
Mild cleanup for passive/urgent version code.
Added an example update script.
added BUILD_VERSION (passive or urgent) to settings.py. Can be overwritten with command line arg.
converted line breaks in vendor/jinja2/LICENSE
Simplified string extraction by piggybacking off Jinja2. Does not rely on gettext anymore. Success.
Added all target languages, as well as currently known fallback languages.
comment fix
